{"tid":1548614,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"9月9號 第一城學生哥要人","createTime":"2019-09-07T05:18:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T15:02:41.000Z","uid":66108,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"952bb3c0d682d5000754ccf56b972b58659f931a","tid":1548614,"uid":66108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T05:18:11.000Z","msg":"上星期舉行左一次聲援罷課行動<br />\n結果不完美但可接受要改善<br />\n途中仲有廢老攻擊學生<br />\n<br />\n第一城眾學校舊生如果仲有良知 唔該9月9號去保護你地啲師弟師妹<br />\n去保護一班係大陸紅底學校仲可以保持到有良知嘅學生<br />\n唔使再諗出黎嘅原因 唔須要有領袖<br />\n你地嘅師弟妹須要保護 就係咁多<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UR5HRxQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUR5HRxQ.jpg&h=10d7ee4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iMb0DcW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiMb0DcW.jpg&h=cccb6c8b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fbd2c660c6a2169a4581965a31f44fc7a423f3cc","tid":1548614,"uid":33382,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T05:25:06.000Z","msg":"全民發起我不自殺聲明運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1548529\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1548529</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">本人xxx，謹此聲明：本人身體健康、思想正面、樂觀開朗、有堅強信念。<br />\nI xxx, hereby declare: I am healthy, positive, optimistic, cheerful, and have strong beliefs.<br />\n<br />\n本人承諾，在過去、現在、將來無論遭遇疾病、政治迫害、艱辛或其他任何情況，都絕不會做出自殺行為。本人除專制暴政以外，並無任何敵人。如本人遭遇不測、自殺、失蹤或任何非自然死亡，包括車禍、溺水等「意外」，均為中共與港共暴政指使加害。特留此存照。<br />\n<br />\nI promise that in the past, present and future, no matter whether I have suffered from illness, political persecution, hardship or any other situation, I will never commit suicide. I have no enemies other than tyranny. If I suffer from accidents, suicides, disappearances or any unnatural deaths, including accidents such as car accidents and drowning, they are all murdered by the CCP and the Hong Kong Communist Government. <br />\n<br />\n#我不自殺聲明<br />\n#NoSuicideStatement<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>麻煩大家係FB/IG tag3個朋友再share出去！麻煩文宣整個我不自殺logo畀人轉FB/ IG icon!!!</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">831 失蹤左幾多個？新屋嶺拉左幾多個？放左幾多個？</span><br />\n<br />\n上個post<br />\n建議發起我不自殺聲明運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1548031\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1548031</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ec9059668844199a63276d9c414d2287ebc5917a","tid":1548614,"uid":66108,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T05:33:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5cf05ccb0037ca4b095ba7930772f57eeaa92c29","tid":1548614,"uid":167536,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T05:36:32.000Z","msg":"推呀，可以拖到女校嘅女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"911f68d99ca1fee829b2029a5252e6e6e4c683c4","tid":1548614,"uid":93195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T05:39:51.000Z","msg":"推，舊生路過"},{"pid":"874b8d5ba0529c2783b79e2b94bf2f80a3fa129c","tid":1548614,"uid":266820,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T05:40:02.000Z","msg":"推唔好比佢沉"},{"pid":"133ecc878b1c809ed519d0343411f09aae8a7d87","tid":1548614,"uid":266820,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T05:40:16.000Z","msg":"推啊 拖手仔啦"},{"pid":"274c04baf17e0286097398025a4c2e8ca9932ac3","tid":1548614,"uid":266820,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T05:40:28.000Z","msg":"早少少起身得唔得"},{"pid":"b3232311d01b68b27d6418a35d11139c80698766","tid":1548614,"uid":266820,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T05:41:09.000Z","msg":"加埋威院學生啊依家"},{"pid":"54170cffee1d627c56ded780eb207e5cbedb903a","tid":1548614,"uid":266820,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T05:41:32.000Z","msg":"支持下cu medic學生"},{"pid":"931b9f711aedc687c1974ba2e7c63ee281b0b8